<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><?ish ishref="GUID-47163028-5130-46C2-9D99-8F0F03EB2B6E" version="2" lang="en-US"?><task xmlns:ditaarch="http://dita.oasis-open.org/architecture/2005/" id="GUID-47163028-5130-46C2-9D99-8F0F03EB2B6E" xml:lang="en-US" ditaarch:DITAArchVersion="1.3" domains="(topic task)                            (topic hi-d)                            (topic ui-d)                            (topic sw-d)                            (topic indexing-d)                            (topic ut-d)                            a(base ishcondition)                            a(base varid)                            a(base varref)                            a(base cid)                            a(base partslist)                            (topic oce-d)                            (topic sdlVariables-c)                            (topic oceCommonElements-c)                            (topic oceMetaDecl-c)                            (topic oceTopic-c)                            (topic oceTopic-c task oceTask-c)                            (topic oceTopic-c hi-d oceHighlight-c)                            (topic oceTopic-c ui-d oceUi-c)                            (topic oceTopic-c sw-d oceSoftware-c)   " class="- topic/topic task/task "><title class="- topic/title ">How to upgrade the ONYX printer driver</title><prolog class="- topic/prolog "><metadata class="- topic/metadata "><category class="- topic/category ">Installation</category></metadata></prolog><taskbody class="- topic/body task/taskbody "><prereq id="GUID-C71E4B56-F6A6-429E-9630-3F0443D53874" class="- topic/section task/prereq "><ul id="UL_5CF05B1DAFBC41A4B310C4B8A0E6A51B" class="- topic/ul "><li id="LI_720890BF721F4E4998FA9AC235FA9E44" class="- topic/li "><p class="- topic/p ">The Colorado M-series requires ONYX 22. 
</p><note id="GUID-15BE2F69-F330-4A94-A42F-8F6DBD35CF35" class="- topic/note "><p class="- topic/p ">The screen dumps in this procedure are of the Colorado M-series. 
</p></note></li><li class="- topic/li "><p class="- topic/p ">Get the newest version of the Colorado M-series PrnInst file. 
</p><p class="- topic/p "> The.prninst file contains a driver and media profiles. 
</p></li><li id="LI_CAC4B2ED6A984A9D90ECACDDA4CDA01F" class="- topic/li "><p class="- topic/p ">Administrator rights within ONYX are required for the driver installation and configuration. 
</p><p class="- topic/p ">If you have to provide administrator credentials when launching ONYX, then they have to be available or the customer has to enter them. 
</p></li><li id="LI_4B03996D878549C7BD5DB682FF4CE807" class="- topic/li "><p class="- topic/p ">No media should be loaded. 
</p></li></ul></prereq><section id="GUID-94C20406-75A1-4BD0-A7DB-8CD9777F04B0" class="- topic/section "><title class="- topic/title ">Upgrade procedure</title><table id="GUID-7E9D9E3B-0708-4F85-993B-CC5E255435C6" pgwide="1" class="- topic/table "><tgroup align="left" outputclass="step" cols="3" class="- topic/tgroup "><colspec colname="col1" colnum="1" colwidth="10*" class="- topic/colspec "/><colspec colname="col2" colnum="2" colwidth="50*" class="- topic/colspec "/><colspec colname="col3" colnum="3" colwidth="40*" class="- topic/colspec "/><thead valign="top" class="- topic/thead "><row class="- topic/row "><entry colname="col1" align="left" valign="top" class="- topic/entry "><p class="- topic/p ">Step 
</p></entry><entry colname="col2" align="left" valign="top" class="- topic/entry "><p class="- topic/p ">Action 
</p></entry><entry colname="col3" align="left" valign="top" class="- topic/entry "><p class="- topic/p ">Remarks 
</p></entry></row></thead><tbody valign="top" class="- topic/tbody "><row class="- topic/row "><entry colname="col1" align="left" valign="top" class="- topic/entry "><p class="- topic/p ">1 
</p></entry><entry colname="col2" align="left" valign="top" class="- topic/entry "><p class="- topic/p ">Make sure that ONYX is not active. If active: de-activate it. 
</p></entry><entry colname="col3" align="left" valign="top" class="- topic/entry "/></row><row class="- topic/row "><entry colname="col1" align="left" valign="top" class="- topic/entry "><p class="- topic/p ">2 
</p></entry><entry colname="col2" align="left" valign="top" class="- topic/entry "><p class="- topic/p ">Select the Colorado M-series PrnInst file and double click it. 
</p><fig id="GUID-D175409C-4FB9-4C2B-9002-719B301AE469" class="- topic/fig "><image href="GUID-29A15AC7-0AE9-45A0-9F81-D8166B788C17-low.png" placement="inline" class="- topic/image " otherprops="GUID-29A15AC7-0AE9-45A0-9F81-D8166B788C17-low.png"/></fig><fig id="FIG_A8E77317EC224D038F95DC484B80B5C7" class="- topic/fig "/></entry><entry colname="col3" align="left" valign="top" class="- topic/entry "/></row><row class="- topic/row "><entry colname="col1" align="left" valign="top" class="- topic/entry "><p class="- topic/p ">3 
</p></entry><entry colname="col2" align="left" valign="top" class="- topic/entry "><p class="- topic/p ">Choose Install, Choose options : 
</p><ul class="- topic/ul "><li class="- topic/li "><p class="- topic/p ">Update Printer 
</p></li><li class="- topic/li "><p class="- topic/p ">Update Driver 
</p></li><li class="- topic/li "><p class="- topic/p "> Append Media 
</p></li><li class="- topic/li "><p class="- topic/p "> Colorado 1650 
</p></li><li class="- topic/li "><p class="- topic/p "> Ignore Duplicates 
</p></li></ul><note id="GUID-AB0F9A99-D741-42AD-B084-DE16B5599DD6" class="- topic/note "><p class="- topic/p ">Append media is an optional action. Some customers have only the media installed that they use. 
</p><p class="- topic/p ">Check with the customer whether media has to be added yes or no . 
</p></note></entry><entry colname="col3" align="left" valign="top" class="- topic/entry "><p class="- topic/p ">The configuration screen shot.
</p><fig id="GUID-1954DB98-7E3F-4687-BA4E-971D919B6908" class="- topic/fig "><image href="GUID-00092442-4CC1-4B92-9D4A-41A2ACB397F8-low.png" placement="inline" class="- topic/image " otherprops="GUID-00092442-4CC1-4B92-9D4A-41A2ACB397F8-low.png"/></fig></entry></row></tbody></tgroup></table></section></taskbody><related-links class="- topic/related-links "><linkpool class="- topic/linkpool " mapkeyref="GUID-8A41CFEA-5928-4042-A2CB-507A5D034160"><link class="- topic/link " mapclass="- map/topicref " format="dita" type="concept" href="generated-topic-GUID-3140D264-493B-4163-8934-73ACCD3B6AA1.xml" role="parent"><?ditaot usertext?><linktext class="- topic/linktext "><?ditaot usertext?>Installation</linktext></link></linkpool></related-links>
